ActCanada Early Learning and Child Care Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Employment and Social Development To Be the Minister for the Purposes of the Canada Early Learning and Child Care Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing the Order in Council P.C. 2024-345 of April 12, 2024; and (2) designating the Minister of EMPLOYMENT AND SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT as the Minister for the Purposes of the CANADA EARLY LEARNING AND CHILD CARE ACT.
